{
  "stem": "23350.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I was looking for Ellen, for the girl who brought me here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I said, what did I need that for?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "To go to Hyde Park, I should not have all this excitement.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "By this time, I was terribly excited, and tears were coming down my face and things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I was hiding from everybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I go down and look around the whole crowd, and everywhere people were scattering and going and this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I can't see Ellen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "She brought me, but she left me there, you know, all alone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I was real-- I couldn't believe that she could do such a thing to me because I wasn't keen to go, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Anyway the end is, I'm standing and waiting and looking in all the directions, and who comes behind me but this old fellow.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And he starts saying to me something like, miss, would you like to come and have a cup of tea?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So I said, I don't drink tea.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I don't speak to strangers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I recognized who he was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I was very cross with him, you know, because I already told him off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I was walking away, and he went away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I thought I would never see him anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then it came around that after-- and I was waiting for this Ellen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't want to go alone Sunday to the hostel to be on my own.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I thought, she must come back for me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She can't leave me here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, again, I went around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "First, I sat down on the bench-- on a bench.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then I got up, then started looking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Couldn't see her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, in the end, he came back again, whether I would like to drink some coffee.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
